  "female_01": {
    "model_name": "amitaro",
    "speaker_id": 0,
    "default_style": "Neutral",
    "style_weight": 2.0,
    "language": "JP",
    "voice_profile": "lumina_female"
  }
}
```

## 8.2 現在の搭載 voice

* `female_01`

## 8.3 将来追加予定

* `male_01`

