## 10. WebSocket API 仕様

## 10.1 エンドポイント

* `WS /sessions`

### 目的

PicoClaw から text delta を逐次受け取り、chunk 単位で音声化する。

---

## 10.2 message: session_start

```json
{
  "type": "session_start",
  "session_id": "sess-001",
  "response_id": "resp-001",
  "voice_id": "female_01",
  "speech_mode": "conversational",
  "context": {
    "event": "conversation",
    "urgency": "normal",
    "conversation_mode": "chat",
    "user_attention_required": false
  }
}
```

---

## 10.3 message: text_delta

```json
{
  "type": "text_delta",
  "session_id": "sess-001",
  "seq": 1,
  "text": "今日はですね、",
  "emitted_at": "2026-03-11T07:40:00+09:00"
}
```

---

## 10.4 message: session_end

```json
{
  "type": "session_end",
  "session_id": "sess-001",
  "is_final": true
}
```

---

## 10.5 message: audio_chunk_ready

```json
{
  "type": "audio_chunk_ready",
  "session_id": "sess-001",
  "chunk_index": 0,
  "text": "今日はですね、",
  "audio_path": "cache/sess-001_000.wav",
  "sample_rate": 44100,
  "pause_after": "short"
}
```

---

## 10.6 message: session_completed

```json
{
  "type": "session_completed",
  "session_id": "sess-001"
}
```

---

## 10.7 message: error

```json
{
  "type": "error",
  "session_id": "sess-001",
  "code": "VOICE_NOT_FOUND",
  "message": "voice_id 'female_99' is not registered"
}
```

